node.text: End of day, Friday was crazy as fuck, but I got some work done, somebody said to me today, I don’t know any black man that have two water front property /restaurant in America, I never think of that, I guess I AM THE SHIT, 😂😂😂🙏🏾🙏🏾💰💰💰💰, let’s go Baltimore, question, did y’all know that 7 out of 10 people in Baltimore is black?  If you didn’t know, that’s why I am here, I ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️y’all. @baronebaltimore I am a little bit nice
